      "role": "user",
      "content": "Those points make sense. It's basically just exploiting human nature. Do you have any advice on how to frame this for employees who might think they're too smart to be tricked? How can I describe the 'vibe' of these attackers to make them realize it's not just a technical error, but a deliberate attempt to mess with them?",
